{"tid":2187660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣協助流亡港人預算將增七倍","createTime":"2020-09-03T18:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T03:45:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0f09eca1828f7dfba9aeb0e82fc202c4e98f0c7d","tid":2187660,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T18:58:58.000Z","msg":"因應中央在香港實施港版國安法，台灣陸委會今年7月設立台港服務交流辦公室，執掌該辦公室的台港策進會今年度的預算大幅增加，比往年大增七倍至4,100萬元新台幣（約1,080萬港元）。陸委會指出，增加的預算將用於港人在台就學就業的生活照顧及輔導。<br />\n<br />\n據台港策進會公佈的年度預算書，明年度預算將提升至4,108萬餘元，比今年度的491萬元新台幣（約130萬港元）急增七倍有多。對於增加預算的安排，邱垂正指，相關預算用在針對港人在台就學就業的生活照顧及輔導等費用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/E4F6BR5MNRC6NNHAMWMV5ETFJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FE4F6BR5MNRC6NNHAMWMV5ETFJA%2F&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=3d15f821\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FE4F6BR5MNRC6NNHAMWMV5ETFJA%2F&h=82acaf34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/E4F6BR5MNRC6NNHAMWMV5ETFJA/</a>"},{"pid":"11254150ebb2636ea33dd329e0ca3a3bdeb3c4e9","tid":2187660,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T19:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfe65d3edaa457313e28b453d3eb161d562c244","tid":2187660,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T19:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx"},{"pid":"88